OL,3,CThis year's Oscars become the first to
OL,4,Cimplement new diversity rules
OL,6,FThe films in the running for best
OL,7,Fpicture must have met two of the four
OL,8,Fnew standards that include at least
OL,9,F30% of actors being from at least two
OL,10,Funderrepresented groups (including
OL,11,Fwomen, race, ethnicity, sexuality and
OL,12,Fdisability), and the main storyline,
OL,13,Ftheme, or narrative must be centered
OL,14,Fon at least one of the aforementioned
OL,15,Fgroups.
OL,17,FOut of the 10 best picture nominees,
OL,18,Ffour are in part or totally in a
OL,19,Fforeign language - including British
OL,20,Fentry .
