OL,3,CThis year's Oscars become the first to
OL,4,Cimplement new diversity rules
OL,6,FThe new diversity and inclusion rules
OL,7,Fcoming into force this year appear to
OL,8,Fhave yielded results - American
OL,9,FFiction, a satire about racial
OL,10,Fpolitics, has five nominations in all,
OL,11,Fincluding one for best film.
OL,13,FBut its director, Cord Jefferson, told
OL,14,FITV News' Arts Editor Nina Nannar that
OL,15,Feven after 2015's viral hashtag
OL,16,F_OscarsSoWhite, the change remains
OL,17,Fslow-moving.
