OL,3,CThis year's Oscars become the first to
OL,4,Cimplement new diversity rules
OL,6,F"I don't think that we are anywhere
OL,7,Fnear where we need to be to get actual
OL,8,Fequity for people of colour in this
OL,9,Findustry but things are getting
OL,10,Fbetter," he said.
OL,12,F"I think the fact that there was a
OL,13,Fgroup of people willing to give me
OL,14,Fmillions of dollars to make this
OL,15,Fmovie, I think is evidence of the fact
OL,16,Fthat things are changing a little bit."
