OL,3,CThis year's Oscars become the first to
OL,4,Cimplement new diversity rules
OL,6,FThis year's Academy Awards are also
OL,7,Fbeing hailed as the first time two
OL,8,Fopenly LGBTQ+ actors have been
OL,9,Fnominated for playing gay characters,
OL,10,FColman Domingo in Rustin and two-time
OL,11,FOscar winner Jodie Foster in Nyad.
OL,13,FMost categories this year include at
OL,14,Fleast one person from an
OL,15,Funderrepresented group, with almost a
OL,16,Fthird of nominees women - a three-year
OL,17,Fhigh.
OL,19,FHowever, when it comes to best
OL,20,Fdirector, only eight women have ever
OL,21,Fhad a nomination.
